    "You can be optionally notified when the amount of insulin in the current Pod drops to a selected level below the current reservoir value of %1$@ units.\n\nSet the low reservoir alert level for the current Pod." : {
      "comment" : "Description text on LowReservoirView for the current Pod (1: current reservoir value"
    },
    "You can be optionally notified when the amount of insulin remaining in the reservoir reaches a selected level (1 - %1$d units).\n\nSet the default low reservoir alert level to configure when pairing a Pod." : {
      "comment" : "Description text on LowReservoirView Default value (1: max value)"
    },
    "You will be notified in advance of Pod expiration.\n\nScroll to set the number of hours advance notice you would like to have." : {
      "comment" : "Description text on ExpirationReminderSetupView",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
